## STOP_SCRIPTED_CONVERSATION

```c
// 0xD79DEEFB53455EBA 0xAB77DA7D
int STOP_SCRIPTED_CONVERSATION(Bool stopNow);
```

```
    Used for stopping scripted conversations
    
```

## Parameters
* **stopNow**: Bool controlling weather the current conversation line should finish before stopping the conversation. 
## Return value
The conversation line that the conversation was on when stopped.
